Create a pyspark program to perform following data processing; 

Stage 1:
========
1. Use 1970movies.json file - assume file to be available in DBFS or S3 for the program.
2. Flatten the JSON file above and create a Dataframe.
3. Write above Dataframe to Delta Lake partitioned by year.
4. Add an adhoc paragraph to restore 7 days back point in time data from Delta Lake.

Stage 2:
========
From the final data in delta lake;

1. Create Movie dimension in Delta lake with movieId.
2. Update delta table created in Stage 1 with movieId corresponding to title.

Solution: Please refer to pyspark_evaluation_1970movie.ipynb notebook
